&lt;li&gt;Identify recurring friction points across customer tickets and turn them into clear product feedback for Product and Engineering&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own day-to-day support for production customers, managing issues that come in through Pylon with urgency, clarity, and strong customer communication&lt;/li&gt;
