&lt;li&gt;Experience working with enterprise customers; particularly in content, marketing or digital operations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Familiarity with LLMs, generative AI pipelines and agent-style automation frameworks.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Background in consulting, technical solution engineering or internal tools engineering.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
